[0.0.4]
- ShaderProgramFiles replaced by ShaderProgramManaged, migration instructions : 
-- create a class annotated by @ShaderInfo (can be an inner static class) containing uniforms variable.
-- enable @Storable option in @ShaderInfo in order to save/load shader file path
-- replace ShaderProgramFiles field by an @Editable non-transient field.
-- update non editable fields before shader begin

[0.0.2]
- use DesktopApplication instead of LwjglApplication in loaders.